name: Apple 30-pin male to VGA female
mainPurpose: For connecting older iPhones and iPads to VGA display.
end1Desc: 30-pin male plugs into iPhone or iPad.
end2Desc: VGA female accepts cable with VGA male that is also plugged into a display device.

name: Apple Lightning Digital AV male to HDMI female, plus Lightning female
mainPurpose: Connect iPhone or iPad to an HDMI display.
end1Desc: Lightning male plugs into iPhone or iPad.
end2Desc: HDMI female accepts a cable with a HDMI male that is also plugged into a display device.
notes: Lightning female accepts male from the Apple device's battery.

name: Apple MiniDisplay male to HDMI female
mainPurpose: Connect Apple laptop with MiniDisplay Port to an HDMI display.
end1Desc: MiniDisplay male plugs into laptop's MiniDisplay Port.
end2Desc: HDMI female accepts a cable with a HDMI male that is also plugged into a display device.

name: HDMI male to HDMI male extension cord
mainPurpose: Reach long distance between HDMI device and a HDMI display.
end1Desc: HDMI male plugs into a computer's HDMI port.
end2Desc: HDMI male plugs into a display's HDMI port.

name: HDMI male to VGA female, plus Micro USB male to USB male
mainPurpose: For connecting devices with HDMI output to a VGA-only display.
end1Desc: HDMI male plugs into a computer.
end2Desc: VGA female connects to a display.
notes: For power, the Micro USB plugs into the adapter and the USB plugs into the device.

name: Micro HDMI male to HDMI female (2 inches)
mainPurpose: Connect Android phones and tablets to a HDMI display.
end1Desc: Micro HDMI male plugs into an Android phone or tablet.
end2Desc: HDMI female accepts a cable with a HDMI male that is also plugged into a display device.

name: Micro HDMI male to HDMI female (six inches)
mainPurpose: Connect Android phones and tablets to a HDMI display.
end1Desc: Micro HDMI male plugs into an Android phone or tablet.
end2Desc: HDMI female accepts a cable with a HDMI male that is also plugged into a display device.

name: VGA male to HDMI female, plus 1/8 inch audio jack, plus Micro USB male to USB male
mainPurpose: Connect devices with VGA output to HDMI display input.
end1Desc: VGA male plugs into device with VGA output.
end2Desc: HDMI female connects to HDMI port on a display.
notes: For power, the Micro USB plugs into the adapter and the USB plugs into the device. For audio, the 1/8 inch audio jack plugs into the device's audio output.
